ntial element of his research.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aAstronomyvEarly works to 1800. 0aDrawingxScientific applications. 4aKunsttheorie. 4aLudovico Cigoli. 4aZeichnung. 7aART / General.2bisacsh  aart theory.  adrawing.1 aMitch, Cohen.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2019z978311071956708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2019z9783110605785oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2019 Englishz978311061001708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE  DG 2019 Englishz978311061685908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG0 cEPUBz97831105383040 cprintz978311052006440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311053921940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110539219423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110539219.jpg  a978-3-11-061001-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061685-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE  DG 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-071956-7  DG Plus eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_ECL_MUAR  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2019  aZDB-23-DPKb2019